The paper focuses on the analysis of academic communication platforms and the metrics available on them, which are relevant to several sub-categories in computer science. The sub-category of Digital Libraries (cs.DL) is the most likely as the paper deals with online academic profiles and their impact. Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI, cs.IR) are also relevant as the paper discusses the use of social media platforms and the analysis of metrics related to academic impact. Cybersecurity (cs.CY) is a possible sub-category as the paper may touch upon issues related to privacy and security of academic profiles. Lastly, Social and Information Networks (cs.SOC) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses the use of social media platforms and their impact on academic communication.
